{
  "stem": "4710.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And everybody just had to put on their hand [NON-ENGLISH] and their hat [NON-ENGLISH] and just have to say the first-- the first chapter of Shema and the next one.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were queuing up hundreds of people for that [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I don't have to do a lot with the Jewish identity as such, because we were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I mean, why--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Jewish life.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, I-- I-- I was eating whatever-- whatever is provided.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- I-- and-- and sometimes-- sometimes, you know, in the evening, with the bread, occasionally, you-- you had a bit of-- bit of-- piece of salami or-- or something.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My brother didn't eat it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I-- I-- I ate it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I-- I thought I have to.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And most important, I realize, is that we are-- we are now in exceptional-- exceptional times.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the main aim in life now is to survive.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And anything else would be subordinate to that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And to be surviving, not only-- not only-- not only forget about Jewish practice, but also forget about that you are a human being.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Anything-- anything which-- which matters in life, if you-- if you start thinking what you are, what happened, then you will just go and electrocute yourself to the-- to the electric wire.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But I thought, I mustn't think about it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I just has to behave like an animal.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Just-- just survival.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Survival to avoid being-- being beaten up, avoid-- try to get as much food like as-- as you can, and just survival.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And everything spiritual comes if you manage to survive.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I had-- I had some great doubts about it at end of the day.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I-- I will survive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Even after when I survived the selections.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
